keep it simple

objective of game: 
    avoid flying objects 
    kill enemies 
    go to next level 

player mechanics
    player can run/jump 
    no lives 
    remain suspended in air for short amount of time 

level mechanics 
    flying objects toward player, one hit kills player 
    enemies have can shoot at player, only damages 
    MAIN GAME MECHANIC:
        Each level will have a mutiple bullets flying
        if can dodge bullets and timer is done, can go to next round, (maybe add enemies)
        POLISH: 
            add circle when shot out 

decor: 
    pillars
    torches
    etc 

Juice: 
    light
    flames 
    backgound movement 
